♪Who am I waiting for♪

162
00:10:18,960 --> 00:10:22,200
♪No right or wrong♪

163
00:10:23,320 --> 00:10:27,400
♪It's God's prank♪

164
00:10:27,840 --> 00:10:32,200
♪Fall into thousands of stars♪

165
00:10:32,480 --> 00:10:36,840
♪Just to look you in the eyes♪

166
00:10:37,080 --> 00:10:40,560
♪Pause again and again♪

167
00:10:40,560 --> 00:10:45,840
♪Something is on the tip
of the tongue♪

168
00:10:46,160 --> 00:10:49,880
♪I thought
I caught the promise♪

169
00:10:49,880 --> 00:10:52,240
♪You're the one who said♪

170
